io.netty.util.concurrent

Interface WrappedEventExecutor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, EventExecutor, EventExecutorGroup, Executor, ExecutorService, ScheduledExecutorService
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    PausableEventExecutor

    public interface WrappedEventExecutor
extends EventExecutor
    A marker interface indicating that the EventExecutor is a wrapper around another EventExecutor implementation. See EventExecutor.unwrap() and PausableEventExecutor for further details.
